INSERT INTO transportation (tripId, type, origin, destination, company, carModel, departureDate, departureTime, arrivalDate, arrivalTime, confirmationNumber, phone, website, price, currency, paymentStatus, notes, createdAt, updatedAt)
SELECT tripId, 'car_rental', pickupLocation, returnLocation, company, carModel, pickupDate, pickupTime, returnDate, returnTime, confirmationNumber, phone, website, price, currency, paymentStatus, notes, createdAt, updatedAt
FROM car_rentals
WHERE id = (SELECT MAX(id) FROM car_rentals);
